::Zardus/Mosquitor/Striker/Zenyak/Shredder/DevilDuer/DeathStorm/FZ/Prowl::

Zardus looks briefly at the predacon base. "I offer an alliance between your 
faction and mine, Hell Beast. You can think it over and give me your answer 
on monday."

He turns away and starts walking. "Nemesis," He says, raising his comm-link 
to his mouth, "You and Wolfgang are in charge untill I get back."

All of a sudden a blue beam hits Zardus and he disapears untill monday (in 
real life).

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Mosquitor looks down at himself in shock as he starts glowing.

"I shall be back on monday." He says right before he dissapears.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Striker walks up to Tigerhawk. "Tell Liono that me and Prowl will be gone for 
the next three days." He says as he and Prowl phase out.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Zenyak climbs out the CR chamber. He blinks in surprise as he is surrounded 
by a glow and dissapears.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shredder growls as he phases out. The corner of the speeder that he was 
carying drops to the ground.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DevilDuer turns around as FZ enters the bridge. His hand accidently hits some 
controlls, phasing himself and FZ out for the next thee days.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DeathStorm's ship glows and disapears, leaving a bare clearing in the forest.
